  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This puzzle game delivers a satisfying experience as you connect grains of the same color and clear them all at once. The more grains you connect, the higher your score when you clear them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.poster.avif?t=1740102095\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.webm?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.mp4?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect grains of the same color to make them disappear. In “ARRANGE” mode, special grains will appear, and in the “+” mode, the stages will expand, giving you more room to play.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.poster.avif?t=1740102095\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.webm?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.mp4?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This puzzle game delivers a satisfying experience as you connect grains of the same color and clear them all at once. The more grains you connect, the higher your score when you clear them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.poster.avif?t=1740102095\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.webm?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/67db762e557e33e0a145e318c355b46b.mp4?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect grains of the same color to make them disappear. In “ARRANGE” mode, special grains will appear, and in the “+” mode, the stages will expand, giving you more room to play.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.poster.avif?t=1740102095\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.webm?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067840/extras/d78a5534b869132c88645ed039d0cbd7.mp4?t=1740102095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
